Package courses

Class Course

java.lang.Object
courses.Course
public final class Course
extends java.lang.Object
This class represents a Course that the student has taken. It contains the documents and assignments associated to itself. This class is final and Immutable.

    • getNewestDocuments

      public courses.CourseDocument[] getNewestDocuments​(int x)
      Sorts the list of documents by time and gets the first x documents by newest date. Will return an empty array if x is 0 or the list is empty.
      Parameters:
      x - The number of documents to get
      Returns:
      Array of the latest documents sorted from oldest to newest

    • getOldestDocuments

      Returns:

    • getAssignments

    • getNewestAssignments

      public courses.CourseAssignment[] getNewestAssignments​(int x)
      Sorts the list of assignments by time and gets the first x assignments by newest date.
      Parameters:
      x - Number of assignments to get.
      Returns:
      An array of the corresponding assignments. It will be ordered from oldest to newest. Note: Will return an empty array if x is 0 or the list is empty.
